Dialogue: 8,0:19:08.00,0:19:12.11,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}试着轻轻触碰我
Dialogue: 8,0:19:12.51,0:19:18.45,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}这颗心属于你
Dialogue: 8,0:19:19.01,0:19:22.24,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}无论何种伤痛
Dialogue: 8,0:19:22.85,0:19:26.44,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}由我替你消除
Dialogue: 8,0:19:26.58,0:19:31.78,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}相信你心中的悸动
Dialogue: 8,0:19:31.78,0:19:36.96,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}那是命运的旋律
Dialogue: 8,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.37,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}我爱今天
Dialogue: 8,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.38,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}我爱今天
Dialogue: 8,0:19:48.38,0:19:53.38,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}因为我们仍活于世 与彼此相遇
Dialogue: 8,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.65,Insert_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}我和你
